y%20it%20has%20for%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20finite%20amount%20of%20cash.%20It%20can%20be%20used%20on%20better%20things%20than%20paying%20down%20the%20interest%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20particularly%20the%20case%20in%20an%20era%20of%20higher%20interest%20rates.%20After%20over%20a%20decade%20of%20historically%20low%20rates%2C%20borrowing%20costs%20are%20up%20again.%20The%20US%20spent%20more%20servicing%20its%20debt%20than%20it%20did%20on%20the%20military%20for%20the%20first%20time%20last%20year%2C%20with%20debt%20service%20amounting%20to%203.1%25%20of%20GDP%20growth%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20factors%20interrelate%2C%20of%20course%3A%20the%20size%20of%20the%20national%20debt%20means%20higher%20borrowing%20costs%20have%20a%20more%20material%20impact%20on%20the%20US%20fiscal%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20analysts%20at%20Impax%20Asset%20Management%20wrote%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226124123e-8ca0-4312-9880-3bd02bc57789%5C%22%3E3.%20A%20worse%20fiscal%20position%20could%20lead%20to%20lower%20investor%20confidence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20borrowing%20and%20deficit%20spending%20could%20lead%20to%20less%20confidence%20that%20the%20US%20is%20the%20safest%20market%20for%20investors'%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernments%20that%20run%20sustained%20deficits%20rely%20on%20creditors'%20confidence%20that%20debts%20will%20be%20serviced%20and%20repaid.%20Large%20structural%20deficits%20and%20rising%20national%20debts%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20default%2C%26quot%3B%20Apex%20said%2C%20though%20it%20added%20that%20a%20default%20for%20the%20US%20is%20still%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20the%20government%20could%20be%20forced%20to%20offer%20higher%20yields%20if%20investors%20ever%20appeared%20hesitant%20to%20keep%20buying%20Treasurys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20played%20out%20to%20a%20degree%20this%20w