mg%20width%3D%5C%225226%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chingford%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682e8c9468a292900801fd30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223641%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIve%20grew%20up%20in%20Chingford%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20London.%3Cp%3Eilbusca%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Paul%20Ive%20was%20born%20on%20February%2027%2C%201967%2C%20in%20Chingford%2C%20England%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20London.%20His%20father%20was%20a%20silversmith%2C%20and%20his%20mother%20was%20a%20psychotherapist.%20While%20attending%20secondary%20school%2C%20Ive%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20dyslexia.%20Ive%20studied%20industrial%20design%20at%20Newcastle%20Polytechnic%2C%20now%20called%20Northumbria%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8b7d6b4-adc4-4412-9463-3d3a77040d4f%5C%22%3EJony%20Ive's%20rise%20at%20Apple%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22steve%20jobs%20jony%20ive%20eddy%20cue%20phil%20schiller%20tony%20fadell%20scott%20forstall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682e8ce0ac40ae2b0c9ebafc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20crew%20left%20to%20right%3A%20Phil%20Schiller%2C%20Tony%20Fadell%2C%20Jony%20Ive%2C%20Steve%20Jobs%2C%20Scott%20Forstall%2C%20Eddy%20Cue%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Sprague%2FRedux%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20stint%20at%20Acme%20Corp.%2C%20Ive%20joined%20Apple%20in%201992.%20Ive%20had%20already%20made%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20by%20then%2C%20and%20it%20took%20Apple's%20design%20leader%2C%20Bob%20Brunner%2C%20years%20to%20recruit%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20joined%2C%20he%20quickly%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20and%20became%20Senior%20VP%20of%20Design%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-jobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESteve%20Jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20CEO%20in%201997.%20Jobs'%20first%20major%20assignment%20for%20Ive%20was%20the%20classic%2C%20candy-colored%20iMac.%20Ive%20went%20on%20to%20lead%20the%20design%20on%20Apple's%20biggest%20products%2C%20including%20the%20iPod%2C%20the%20iPhone%2C%20and%20the%20iPad.%20Ive%20maintained%20creative%20oversight%20over%20the%20design%20of%20Apple's%20products%20and%20worked%20with%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20to%20launch%20new%20products%20like%20the%20Apple%20Watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Jobs%20was%20famously%20tough%20to%20get%20along%20with%2C%20Ive%20has%20said%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-jony-ive-what-working-with-steve-jobs-was-like-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20years%20at%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20with%20Jobs.%20Ive%20described%20his%20time%20working%20with%20Jobs%20at%20Apple%20from%201997%20to%202011%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20joyful%20and%20extraordinary%2015%20years%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20said%20the%20two%20ate%20lunch%20together%20%26quot%3Bevery%20day%20of%20the%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20went%20on%20family%20vacations%2C%20and%20had%20continuous%20conversations%20about%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202015%2C%20Ive%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20role%20of%20chief%20design%20officer%20at%20Apple.%20From%202015%20to%202017%2C%20Ive%20focused%20on%20Apple's%20new%20headquarters%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-park%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bspaceship%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20which%20he%20designed%20most%20of%20the%20little%20details.%20Ive%20regained%20direct%20control%20of%20Apple's%20design%20team%20in%202017.%20In%20June%202019%2C%20Apple%20announced%20that%20Ive%20was%20leaving%20the%20company%20after%2027%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIve%20said%20he%20left%20because%20the%20projects%20he'd%20been%20working%20closely%20on%20were%20completed%2C%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjony-ive-leaves-apple-to-form-design-company-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20the%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time.%20He%20also%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20part%20of%20the%20timing%20for%20LoveFrom%20is%20in%20some%20ways%20connected%20to%20having%20a%20very%20clear%20sense%20about%20the%20health%20and%20vitality%20of%20the%20design%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Ives%20said%20to%20the%20financial%20newspaper.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20actually%20looking%20forward%20to%20contributing%20in%20a%20different%20way%20to%20projects%20we've%20been%20working%20together%20on%20for%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20many%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204cc25a5-ec73-4303-b8db-49bf1e2c72a6%5C%22%3EIve's%20design%20philosophy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cornerstone%20of%20Ive's%20success%20is%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F7-philosophies-of-apple-designer-jony-ive-2014-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunique%20design%20philosophy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20at%20Apple%2C%20Ive%20led%20the%20design%20of%20iconic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-mac-products-great-classic-boring-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20the%20iMac%20in%201998%2C%20iPhone%20in%202007%2C%20and%20Apple%20Watch%20in%202014%20%E2%80%94%20shaping%20everything%20from%20hardware%20and%20software%20to%20packaging%2C%20retail%20stores%2C%20and%20even%20Apple's%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIve%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Stripe%20CEO%20Patrick%20Collison%20that%20his%20ideas%20and%20work%20at%20Apple%20were%20often%20inspired%20by%20Dieter%20Rams%2C%20the%20German%20industrial%20designer%20who%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bless%20but%20better%26quot%3B%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20said%20that%20whenever%20he%20starts%20working%20on%20a%20project%2C%20he%20thinks%20about%20the%20utility%20of%20a%20product%20and%20then%20he%20begins%20to%20consider%20what%20it%20will%20actually%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20research.%20To%20ensure%20he%20created%20the%20right%20color%20tones%20for%20the%20iMac%2C%20Ive%20talked%20with%20jelly%20bean%20manufacturers.%20To%20learn%20how%20to%20make%20super-thin%20metal%20for%20laptops%2C%20he%20sought%20out%20Japanese%20metalworkers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20he%20makes%20products%20that%20care%20about%20functionality%20and%20design.%20In%20a%20profile%20of%20Ive%20in%20Time%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20surrounded%20by%20anonymous%2C%20poorly%20made%20objects.%20It's%20tempting%20to%20think%20it's%20because%20the%20people%20who%20use%20them%20don't%20care%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20the%20people%20who%20make%20them.%20But%20what%20we've%20shown%20is%20that%20people%20do%20care.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20aesthetics.%20They%20care%20about%20things%20that%20are%20thoughtfully%20conceived%20and%20well-made.%20We%20make%20and%20sell%20a%20very%2C%20very%20large%20number%20of%20(hopefully)%20beautiful%2C%20well-made%20things.%20Our%20success%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20purity%2C%20integrity%20%E2%80%94%20for%20giving%20a%20damn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228757a8d9-ae60-4470-b94b-e9932d2cecd2%5C%22%3ECareer%20post-Apple%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIve%20launched%20his%20own%20independent%20design%20company%20called%20LoveFrom%20in%202019%20with%20his%20fellow%20designer%20Marc%20Newson.%20The%20company%20counted%20Apple%20and%20Airbnb%20among%20its%20early%20clients.%20Ive%20and%20LoveFrom%20plan%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20OpenAI%20but%20remain%20independent%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Ive%20launched%20io%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20joint%20project%20between%20LoveFrom%20and%20OpenAI%2C%20Wired%20reported.%20In%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20Io%20and%20OpenAI%20agreed%20for%20OpenAI%20to%20receive%20a%2023%25%20stake%20in%20io.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it's%20fully%20acquiring%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20became%20clear%20that%20our%20ambitions%20to%20develop%2C%20engineer%2C%20and%20manufacture%20a%20new%20family%20of%20products%20demanded%20an%20entirely%20new%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20and%20Ive%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20OpenAI's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235924431-54dd-47ab-992a-3a1d61c33eb6%5C%22%3EAwards%20and%20recognition%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIve%20has%20received%20numerous%20design%20awards%20and%20honorary%20degrees%20for%20this%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202012%20he%20was%20named%20a%20Knight%20Commander%20of%20the%20Order%20of%20the%20British%20Empire%20for%20his%20contributions%20to%20design.%20He%20was%20knighted%20in%20Buckingham%20Palace%20by%20Princess%20Anne%2C%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II's%20only%20daughter%20and%20said%20the%20experience%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20thrilling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20received%20awards%2C%20including%20San%20Francisco%20MoMA's%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%2C%20Inaugural%20Medal%2C%20the%20Benjamin%20Franklin%20Medal%2C%20the%20President's%20Award%2C%20the%20Royal%20Academy%20of%20Engineering's%20President's%20Medal%2C%20and%20the%20Cooper-Hewitt%20National%20Design%20Museum's%20Product%20Design%20Award.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20holds%20honorary%20degrees%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b137b363-77d5-4d96-a8c4-5a8e11ae4ec2%5C%22%3EPersonal%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20London%20native%2C%20Ive%20now%20lives%20near%20Apple's%20headquarters%2C%20having%20purchased%20a%20%2417%20million%2C%20four-bedroom%20home%20in%20Pacific%20Heights%20%E2%80%94%20on%20a%20stretch%20known%2C%20fittingly%2C%20as%20%26quot%3BBillionaire's%20Row.%26quot%3B%20He's%20also%20frequently%20spotted%20at%20local%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20tech%20executives%2C%20he%20owns%20a%20beach%20house%20on%20the%20Hawaiian%20island%20of%20Kauai.%20A%20lifelong%20car%20enthusiast%2C%20Ive%20once%20helped%20his%20father%20restore%20an%20Austin-Healey%20Sprite%2C%20maintains%20a%20personal%20collection%2C%20and%20even%20bought%20Steve%20Jobs'%20former%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsir-jony-ive%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747927476000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682e60edac40ae2b0c9eb9e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsir-jony-ive%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jony%20Ive's%20career%20was%20mainly%20at%20Apple%2C%20designing%20products%20like%20the%20iPhone%20and%20Mac.%20Now%20he'll%20work%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20bought%20his%20AI%20device%20startup%20io.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Canales%2CPaige%20Leskin%2CRebecca%20Aydin%2CLakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsir-jony-ive%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%E2%80%99s%20%245%20mn%20gold%20card%20visa%20to%20be%20launched%3F%20US%20Comm%20Secry%20provides%20update%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747927257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121344083%2Cimgsize-846707.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Fwhen-will-trumps-5-million-gold-card-visa-be-launched-us-commerce-secretary-lutnick-provides-big-update%2Farticleshow%2F121344096.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Commerce%20Secretary%20announced%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bgold%20card%26quot%3B%20visa%20program%2C%20initiated%20by%20President%20Trump%2C%20aimed%20at%20attracting%20wealthy%20international%20investors.%20Requiring%20a%20%245%2