onstruction%20costs%2C%20among%20other%20capabilities.%20%26quot%3BFika%26quot%3B%20means%20%26quot%3Bto%20arrive%26quot%3B%20in%20Swahili.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20also%20teamed%20up%20with%20Better%20Planet%20Laboratory%20to%20create%20WaterNet%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-robotics-predictive-maintenance-manufacturing-factory-solutions-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAI%20model%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20maps%20the%20world's%20waterways.%20They%20used%20satellite%20data%20to%20detect%20elevation%20and%20vegetation%20patterns%2C%20which%20the%20AI%20model%20then%20analyzed%20to%20approximate%20the%20location%20of%20waterways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBridges%20to%20Prosperity%20is%20using%20these%20programs%20with%20governments%20in%20Rwanda%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Uganda%2C%20and%20Zambia%20to%20help%20plan%20bridge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-for-worker-site-safety-in-construction-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econstruction%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20improve%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221364%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nivi%20Sharma%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682c81fb3fe8d39283664dcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221023%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENivi%20Sharma%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Bridges%20to%20Prosperity.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Bridges%20to%20Prosperity%2FShotbygib%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f41d64b1-5d92-43f5-aa81-3000b1bdd421%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELayering%20the%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBridges%20to%20Prosperity%20had%20already%20been%20producing%20maps%20for%20areas%20where%20it%20had%20built%20bridges.%20This%20gave%20the%20NGO%20a%20starting%20database%20of%20geographical%20data%20that%20it%20could%20use%20and%20add%20to%20in%20order%20to%20build%20these%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20easy%20to%20map%20where%20communities%20live%20by%20looking%20at%20satellite%20data%2C%20and%20most%20governments%20have%20schools%2C%20health%20clinics%2C%20markets%2C%20and%20critical%20destinations%20already%20mapped%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20we%20started%20layering%20all%20this%20information%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20used%20data%20from%20less%20conventional%20sources%2C%20like%20the%20fitness%20tracking%20app%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-strava%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrava%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20calculate%20travel%20times%20over%20uneven%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20still%20struggled%20to%20identify%20smaller%20rivers%20and%20streams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHigh-resolution%20satellite%20images%20are%20needed%20for%20the%20mapping%20of%20waterways%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marouane%20Temimi%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Civil%2C%20Environmental%20and%20Ocean%20Engineering%20at%20the%20Stevens%20Institute%20of%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETemimi%20said%20there%20are%20two%20types%20of%20satellite%20data.%20For%20optical%20satellite%20data%2C%20cameras%20capture%20images%20of%20the%20Earth's%20surface.%20Clouds%20can%20disrupt%20this%2C%20blocking%20out%20target%20areas.%20Radar%20satellite%20imagery%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20uses%20radio%20waves%2C%20which%20means%20it%20can%20create%20images%20even%20when%20clouds%20are%20in%20the%20way.%20But%20it%20can%20be%20affected%20by%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20types%20of%20data%20can%20be%20combined%20to%20build%20accurate%20maps%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20come%20with%20a%20cost.%20Temimi%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falbedo-satellite-space-funding-round-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esatellite%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20usually%20collected%20by%20commercial%20sensors%2C%20so%20getting%20the%20information%20can%20be%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESharma%20said%20the%20NGO%20had%20to%20balance%20getting%20quality%20data%20with%20making%20sure%20both%20programs%20were%20affordable%2C%20scalable%2C%20and%20global.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20argument%20around%20AI%20and%20its%20inclusiveness%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20built%20with%20enough%20good%20training%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20often%20overlooks%20the%20entire%20Global%20South%2C%20which%20is%20obviously%20what%20we're%20trying%20not%20to%20do.%20But%20that's%20the%20expensive%20part.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20dashboard%20for%20Fika%20Map%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682b4857c6ad288d14814c6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFika%20Map%20uses%20geographical%20data%20to%20map%20rural%20regions%20and%20identify%20infrastructure%20gaps.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Bridges%20to%20Prosperity%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ce74998-3ea0-4ae3-b64f-2ed489470055%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20tool%20for%20change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBridges%20to%20Prosperity%20and%20Better%20Planet%20Laboratory%20measured%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20dataset%20by%20assessing%20the%20number%20of%20waterways%20identified.%20Previously%2C%20they%20estimated%20that%20there%20were%2054%20million%20kilometers%20of%20mapped%20waterways%20around%20the%20globe.%20The%20WaterNet%20database%20mapped%20another%20124%20million%20kilometers%2C%20or%2077%20million%20miles%2C%20which%20more%20than%20tripled%20the%20number%20of%20known%20waterways%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESharma%20said%20that%20Fika%20Map%20and%20WaterNet%20could%20help%20governments%20complete%20surveying%20work%20for%20bridge%20construction%20in%20months%2C%20rather%20than%20years.%3C%2Fp