slikes%20millennial%20gray%20kitchens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20looks%20so%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20as%20gray%20can%20look%20%26quot%3Bcold%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20kitchen.%20Harsh%20lighting%20can%20create%20the%20same%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20lighting%20is%20very%20cold%20or%20if%20you're%20doing%20all%20neutral%20but%20everything%20feels%20very%20cold%20and%20has%20a%20cold%20undertone%2C%20I%20think%20that%20can%20really%20cheapen%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BGenerally%2C%20the%20spaces%20that%20feel%20the%20most%20luxurious%20and%20welcoming%20are%20warmer%20spaces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224163%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20all-white%20kitchen%20with%20stainless%20steel%20appliances.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673b7870ede4eeae39283133%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20lack%20of%20color%20in%20your%20kitchen%20can%20make%20it%20look%20cheap.%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Hendrickson%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40julianaghani%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuliana%20Ghani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20interior%20designer%20from%20Minneapolis%2C%20tries%20to%20avoid%20too%20much%20gray%2C%20black%2C%20white%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Banything%20that%20looks%20sterile%26quot%3B%20in%20kitchens.%20She%20said%20LED%20light%20bulbs%20are%20a%20huge%20no-no%20for%20her%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20looks%20like%20an%20operating%20room%20when%20you%20have%20those%20blue%20LED%20lights%20on%20your%20island%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20warm%20lighting%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20easiest%20way%20to%20make%20your%20kitchen%20look%20richer%20and%20homey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20bring%20more%20color%20into%20your%20kitchen%2C%20Ghani%20said%20darker%20tones%2C%20like%20aubergine%2C%20ol