let%20panels%20you%20use%20can%20make%20the%20space%20feel%20less%20luxurious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20kitchen%20can%20be%20really%20nice%2C%20and%20then%20if%20I%20see%20cup%20handles%20or%20something%2C%20immediately%20I'm%20just%20like%2C%20'Oh%20gosh%2C%20that%20really%20just%20cheapens%20the%20whole%20feel%20of%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Eustace%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20curved%20handles%20that%20don't%20look%20high-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpgrading%20your%20hardware%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20give%20your%20kitchen%20a%20luxurious%20feel%2C%20though.%20Ghani%20recommends%20brushed%20chrome%2C%20brushed%20nickel%2C%20or%20lacquered%20brass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222de7866a-731c-44e7-bdf9-1960d4e2ebe8%5C%22%3EToo%20much%20on%20the%20counters%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGhani%20said%20that%20too%20many%20items%20on%20your%20counters%20can%20look%20%26quot%3Bmessy%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bcluttered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20cookbooks%20or%20appliances%20you%20use%20daily%20on%20your%20countertops%20can%20help%20a%20space%20look%20lived%20in.%20Eustace%20agreed%2C%20saying%20you%20don't%20want%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkitchen-designs-that-dont-age-well-according-to-interior-designers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyour%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20look%20uninviting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20an%20obsession%20these%20days%20with%20having%20everything%20hidden%2C%20as%20if%20it's%20like%20a%20showroom%20the%20whole%20time%20and%20no%20one%20lives%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Eustace%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20people%20should%20be%20afraid%20to%20have%20things%20out%20or%2C%20you%20know%2C%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20mess%20or%20clutter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20that%20you're%20actually%20using%20every%20day%2C%20and%20just%20signs%20of%20life%2C%20don't%20make%20it%20look%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20though%20she%20said%20microwaves%20sitting%20on%20a%20counter%20aren't%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20in%20her%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kitchen%20appliances%20sitting%20on%20a%20brown%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665f2f72cc442a2f676dc065%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKitchen%20appliances%20sitting%20out%20can%20look%20cheap.%3Cp%3EPixel-Shot%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20to%20make%20sense%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghani%20agreed%20about%20what%20sits%20on%20your%20countertops.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20obnoxious%20if%20you%20eat%20toast%20every%20day%20and%20you%20have%20to%20take%20out%20your%20toaster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20doing%20a%20custom%20kitchen%20or%20you're%20remodeling%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20we%20try%20to%20fit%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-homeowners-adding-second-kitchens-to-houses-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20butler's%20pantry%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20a%20walk-in%20pantry%20where%20you%20can%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20countertop%20appliances%2C%20your%20sugar%2C%20and%20your%20salt%20and%20pepper%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghani%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20both%20designers%20advised%20people%20not%20to%20be%20afraid%20to%20bring%20their%20own%20personality%20to%20their%20spaces%2C%20as%20a%20homey%20kitchen%20is%20the%20best%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-youre-making-your-kitchen-look-cheap-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747919641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682e2ecb68a292900801f657%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-youre-making-your-kitchen-look-cheap