ity%20approaches%20by%20emphasising%20micro-level%20interventions%2C%20small%20yet%20consistent%20actions%20by%20individuals%20and%20communities%20that%20aggregate%20into%20systemic%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20rooting%20change%20in%20local%20realities%2C%20LiFE%20enhances%20existing%20sustainability%20frameworks%20like%20SDG%2011%20and%20the%20New%20Urban%20Agenda%2C%20creating%20a%20bridge%20between%20high-level%20policy%20ambitions%20and%20grassroots%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20distinguishes%20LiFE%20is%20its%20origin%20as%20a%20grassroots%20movement%20in%20India%20that%20has%20evolved%20into%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20national%20environmental%20policy.%20Through%20examples%20like%20the%20eco-village%20of%20Piplantri%2C%20the%20initiative%20shows%20how%20community-led%20actions%20can%20significantly%20advance%20sustainability%20outcomes.%20Importantly%2C%20LiFE%20reframes%20the%20role%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20not%20as%20a%20standalone%20solution%20but%20as%20an%20enabler%20of%20sustainable%20behaviours%2C%20with%20success%20dependent%20on%20community%20participation%20and%20behavioural%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20urban%20centres%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20this%20integrated%20approach%20is%20already%20taking%20shape.%20Community-driven%20lake%20restorations%20and%20youth-led%20mobility%20hackathons%20illustrate%20how%20co-creation%20and%20shared%20responsibility%20are%20becoming%20central%20to%20environmental%20stewardship.%20These%20efforts%2C%20modest%20in%20scale%20but%20rich%20in%20civic%20intent%2C%20mark%20a%20cultural%20realignment%20where%20sustainability%20is%20increasingly%20embedded%20in%20the%20routines%20and%20choices%20of%20everyday%20urban%20life.%3C%