the.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20global%20labs%20to%20local%20streets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20make%20our%20cities%20cleaner%2C%20our%20air%20safer%2C%20and%20our%20communities%20stronger%3F%20After%20spending%20over%20a%20decade%20working%20in%20laboratories%2C%20classrooms%2C%20field%20projects%2C%20and%20ministries%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20answers%20lie%20not%20only%20in%20data%20or%20policy%20but%20also%20in%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20from%20academic%20labs%20in%20the%20UK%20(University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20Guildford)%2C%20Australia%20(Macquarie%20University%2C%20Sydney)%2C%20South%20Korea%20(Gwangju%20Institute%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology)%2C%20and%20the%20US%20(University%20of%20Toledo%2C%20Ohio)%20to%20the%20bustling%20lanes%20of%20Delhi%20(TRIPP%20IIT%20Delhi)%20and%20Aligarh%20(Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20Aligarh%2C%20UP)%20has%20taught%20me%20that%20urban%20sustainability%20is%20not%20just%20a%20scientific%20puzzle%20but%20a%20deeply%20human%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20piece%2C%20I%20want%20to%20share%20the%20lessons%20I%E2%80%99ve%20gathered%20through%20research%2C%20risk%2C%20and%20real-world%20engagement%20about%20how%20cleaner%20air%20and%20more%20livable%20cities%20are%20not%20distant%20dreams%20but%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20hidden%20emergency%20in%20our%20breath%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20knock%20on%20your%20door.%20It%20seeps%20in%20quietly%E2%80%94through%20windows%2C%20lungs%2C%20and%20childhoods.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20contributes%20to%20nearly%20one%20in%20every%20ten%20deaths.%20During%20my%20PhD%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20groups%E2%80%94babies%20in%20prams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20findings%20were%20startling%3A%20children%20in%20prams%20are%20exposed%20to%20up%20to%2060%25%20more%20pollutants%20than%20adults.%20Their%20breathing%20height%20puts%20them%20right%20in%20line%20with%20vehicle%20exhaust.%20Some%20children%20face%20up%20to%2072%25%20higher%20pollution%20levels%20simply%20based%20on%20where%20they%20sit%20in%20a%20double%20pram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20knowledge%20alone%20isn%E2%80%99t%20power.%20Action%20is.%20So%20we%20created%20practical%2C%20scalable%20interventions%E2%80%94pram%20covers%2C%20urban%20route%20mapping%2C%20low-cost%20sensors%E2%80%94and%20tested%20them%20in%20real-world%20conditions.%20The%20Mitigating%20Air%20Pollution%20Exposure%20(MAPE)%20project%2C%20funded%20by%20UKRI%2C%20was%20not%20just%20a%20research%20study.%20It%20became%20a%20guide%20for%20urban%20parents%20navigating%20toxic%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20insights%20shaped%20public%20conversations%2C%20informed%20policies%2C%20and%2C%20perhaps%20most%20importantly%2C%20gave%20families%20the%20tools%20to%20protect%20their%20children%20now%2C%20not%20just%20in%20the%20distant%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20in%20prams%20breathe%20up%20to%2060%25%20more%20pollutants%20than%20adults%20%E2%80%94%20and%20up%20to%2072%25%20more%20in%20double%20prams%2C%20simply%20due%20to%20their%20height%20and%20position%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-435346%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDuring%20his%20PhD%2C%20Dr%20Ashish%20found%20that%20babies%20in%20prams%20inhale%20up%20to%2060%25%20more%20pollution%20than%20adults.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%2C%20together%20with%20his%20PhD%20supervisor%20Prof.%20Prashant%20Kumar%2C%20was%20featured%20during%20a%20BBC%20visit%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%20campus%2C%20highlighting%20their%20innovative%20experimental%20setup%20for%20air%20pollution%20monitoring%20using%20electric%20bike%20trailers.%20Prof.%20Prashant%20Kumar%20is%20the%20Co-Director%20of%20the%20Institute%20for%20Sustainability%2C%20Professor%20and%20Chair%20in%20Air%20Quality%20and%20Health%2C%20and%20Founding%20Dir